Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides Bowling Alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I have a query about my recent billing statement.

I'd be happy to help with that. Could you please provide me with your name?

Sure, my name is Jamie Anderson.

Thank you, Jamie. To access your billing information, could you please provide me with your customer ID number?

Yes, my customer ID is five six seven eight nine.

Great, thank you. And could you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number on file?

The last four digits are one two three four.

Perfect, Jamie. I see your recent bill, and it looks like there's been a late fee applied. Would you like me to go over the details with you?

Yes, that would be helpful. Thanks.

You're welcome. The late fee was applied because the payment was posted two days after the due date. However, I can waive this fee as a one-time courtesy. Would you like me to do that?

Yes, please. That would be great.

All set, Jamie. The fee has been waived. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that's all. Thanks for your help, Alex.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thanks for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
